text: Swalwell is a small village in Kneehill County, Alberta, Canada. It is about from Calgary, the largest city in the Province of Alberta. Swalwell is at . It has a population of 93 people (as of 2021). The postal code in Swalwell is T0M 1Y0. == References == Category:Settlements in Alberta Category:Villages in North America
